America Pop Inc said it plans to buildwith its joint venture partner, Puissant Group, a 2.6 mln dlrs120-unit Days Inn Motor Lodge at the Ohio State Fairgrounds inColumbus. Construction is expected to be completed in lateOctober.    The company also said it plans to complete by mid-October,construction of a 60-unit Days Inn in Athens, Ohio, and byNovember a 60-unit Days Inn Motor Lodge in Green Castle,Pennsylvania. These two projects are organized as limitedpartnerships, it said. Reuter&#3;